question:
District category contains Tech Park, High School Zone, and Silicon Valley.
Supermarkets category contains Family Dollar, Loblaws, and Auchan.
Product category contains Flavored Water, Rice Cakes, Granola Bars, and Canned Broth.
Ingredient category contains Tahini, Amaranth, and Margarine.
The number of each Auchan 's Flavored Water equals each High School Zone 's Product.
The number of each Loblaws 's Granola Bars equals each Granola Bars 's Ingredient.
The number of each High School Zone 's Family Dollar equals 16.
The number of each Loblaws 's Rice Cakes equals 11 more than the sum of each High School Zone 's Product, each Silicon Valley 's Auchan, and each Family Dollar 's Canned Broth.
The number of each Family Dollar 's Rice Cakes equals each Rice Cakes 's Tahini.
The number of each Flavored Water 's Tahini equals 10.
The number of each Silicon Valley 's Auchan equals 5 more than each Family Dollar 's Canned Broth.
The number of each Granola Bars 's Tahini equals 18.
The number of each Family Dollar 's Canned Broth equals 5.
The number of each Loblaws 's Canned Broth equals 10.
The number of each Family Dollar 's Flavored Water equals 6 more than the sum of each Silicon Valley 's Auchan, each Canned Broth 's Tahini, and each Family Dollar 's Canned Broth.
The number of each Canned Broth 's Tahini equals 7 times the difference of each Family Dollar 's Canned Broth and each Silicon Valley 's Auchan.
The number of each Auchan 's Rice Cakes equals 9 times each Granola Bars 's Ingredient.
The number of each Rice Cakes 's Tahini equals the sum of each Auchan 's Rice Cakes and each Granola Bars 's Ingredient.
The number of each Tech Park 's Auchan equals the sum of each Canned Broth 's Ingredient, each Rice Cakes 's Ingredient, and each Family Dollar 's Product.
How many Rice Cakes does Family Dollar have?
solution:
Define each Granola Bars 's Tahini as F; So F = 18.
Define each Granola Bars 's Ingredient as b; So b = F = 18.
Define each Auchan 's Rice Cakes as q; So q = 9 * b = 9 * 18 = 1.
Define each Rice Cakes 's Tahini as P; So P = q + b = 1 + 18 = 19.
Define each Family Dollar 's Rice Cakes as C; So C = P = 19.
